{"title":"艰苦奋斗永不忘","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1966,"month":2,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦奋斗永不忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统永不忘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有房子睡草原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"盖天铺地头枕砖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传统永不忘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋发图强建油田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好管家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"油田就是咱的家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一钉一木要爱它，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由少成多靠积累，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们要当好管家。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起大榔头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起大榔头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸得黄土冒油；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挥汗如淌雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土墙转眼过头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抡起大榔头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砸得土坚墙厚；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今朝住进“干打垒”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过红瓦高楼！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜困难建油田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油工人学毛选，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍天涯不畏难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白云繁星当锦被，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草坪当床抱膝眠。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人立下愚公志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战胜困难建油田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节约资金把油搞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钢筋水泥全不要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只用土草作材料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就地取材干打垒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"节约资金把油搞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传家宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草鞋针线包，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命传家宝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到它不忘本，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干劲高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要的是勤俭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想的是集体，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干的是革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱的是劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要的是勤俭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学红军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石油工人不怕难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要学红军爬雪山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕地冻三尺厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲就是破冰船。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}